data.name: lblDescription.Text
data.value: Before we begin, we need these 4 files to setup the launcher. They must be specifically those files with the given names. They're the Console BIOS and the game ROM. -Required BIOS: SCPH-7003. -Required Game ROM version: SLUS-00067 (2 bin, 1 cue) If you don't have them, you can probably find them online somewhere. Please don't ask for them in the discord as distributing these files is not legal and therefore not allowed there. Upon pressing Confirm, the latest version of LiveSplit, Bizhawk and SotN Rando Tools will be installed.
